seed: Looks awesome! And nice work everyone to catch up on the Referenda!

default.text:
'Cockroach Plushie'

In Referendum 221 the community voted on whether to upgrade the Encointer runtime to v8. As a common-good parachain, the Encointer runtime can only be upgraded through Kusama Governance. Amongst other things, this upgrade also fixes a critical bug.
